snippet.title: DOOM: The Gallery Experience Speedrun - 100% Secrets, Items, Cheese, Beer [2:47/FULLCHUG/NOSPEND]
snippet.description:
Hey there this is Mr Icarus and today I am going to show you how to speedrun art through the medium of DOOM.

FUN FACTS: 
DOOM: The Gallery Experience is actually created using Construct.

Each art has a hyperlink to an actual Metropolitan Museum of Art Page

I don't know how to turn off the message bugging me about my cursor.
